      "media": "https:\/\/drive.google.com\/open?id=1sucGQq6I-asPm3v8EB38kYV8lvO3yLyu",
      "date": "",
      "time": "",
      "description": "<p>Le court-m\u00e9trage a \u00e9t\u00e9&nbsp;r\u00e9alis\u00e9 dans divers lieux de&nbsp;la rue Jean-Talon, entre Saint-Michel et Pie-IX.<\/p>",
