        "title": "O\u00f9 Saint-Henri tape la pierre et tisse l'acier",
        "thumbnail": "http:\/\/staging-lrsm.anagraph.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/Capture-d\u2019e\u0301cran-2017-12-11-a\u0300-12.37.01-150x150.png",
